name: InitializeGAVotersImportTable2
rule:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `Voters_import` (
  `CountyCode` varchar(3) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL,
  `RegistrationNbr` varchar(8) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL,
  `VoterStatus` varchar(1) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `VoterLastName` varchar(20) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `VoterFirstName` varchar(20) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `VoterMiddleMaiden` varchar(20) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `VoterNameSuffix` varchar(3) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `VoterNameTitle` varchar(3) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `ResHouseNbr` varchar(6) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `ResStreetName` varchar(30) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `ResStreetSuffix` varchar(2) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `ResAptUnitNbr` varchar(8) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `ResCityName` varchar(17) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `ResZip` varchar(5) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `ResZipPlus4` varchar(4) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `MidrFlag` varchar(1) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `PollWorker` varchar(1) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `TransactionCode` varchar(1) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `TransactionYearMonth` varchar(6) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `Filler1` varchar(2) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `DateOfBirth` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `RegistrationDate` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `Race` varchar(1) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `Gender` varchar(1) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `Absentee` varchar(1) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `LandDistrict` varchar(3) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `LandLot` varchar(4) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `OriginalRegDate` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `StatusReason` varchar(9) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `Filler2` varchar(5) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `CountyPrecinctId` varchar(5) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `CityPrecinctId` varchar(5) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `CongressionalDistrict` varchar(3) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `SenateDistrict` varchar(3) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `HouseDistrict` varchar(3) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `JudicialDistrict` varchar(3) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `CommDistrict` varchar(3) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `SchoolDistrict` varchar(3) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `CountyDistAName` varchar(13) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `CountyDistAValue` varchar(3) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `CountyDistBName` varchar(13) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `CountyDistBValue` varchar(3) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `MunicipalName` varchar(17) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `MunicipalCode` varchar(3) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `WardCityCouncilName` varchar(13) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `WardCityCouncil` varchar(3) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `CitySchoolDistName` varchar(13) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `CitySchoolDist` varchar(3) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `CityDistAName` varchar(13) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `CityDistAValue` varchar(3) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `CityDistBName` varchar(13) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `CityDistBValue` varchar(3) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `CityDistCName` varchar(13) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `CityDistCValue` varchar(3) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `CityDistDName` varchar(13) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `CityDistDValue` varchar(3) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `DateLastVotedDate` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `TypeOfElection` varchar(3) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `PartyLastVoted` varchar(1) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `LastContactDate` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `MailHouseNbr` varchar(6) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `MailStreetName` varchar(30) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `MailStreetSuffix` varchar(2) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `MailAptUnitNbr` varchar(8) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `MailCity` varchar(17) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `MailState` varchar(2) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `MailZip` varchar(5) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `MailZipPlus4` varchar(4) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `Filler3` varchar(2) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `MailAddress2` varchar(30) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `MailAddress3` varchar(30) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `MailCounty` varchar(20) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `DateAdded` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `DateChanged` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `DistrictCombo` varchar(3) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `ResBuilding` varchar(3) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `MailRRPOBox` varchar(8) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `CombinedStreetAddr` varchar(60) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `ExportDate` date NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`CountyCode`,`RegistrationNbr`,`ExportDate`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 COLLATE=utf8_unicode_ci
